sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant API as VELO API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Stripe as Stripe
    participant Bot as Telegram Bot

    Note over U,Bot: User Journey: Запись на практику

    %% 1. Browse practices
    U->>API: GET /practices?date_from=...
    API->>DB: SELECT practices WHERE...
    DB-->>API: practices list
    API-->>U: [Practice cards]

    %% 2. View details
    U->>API: GET /practices/{id}
    API->>DB: SELECT practice + pricing
    DB-->>API: practice details
    API-->>U: [Practice details page]

    %% 3. Check balance
    Note over U,API: User checks if enough balance
    U->>API: GET /users/me
    API->>DB: SELECT user balance
    DB-->>API: balance_user = $30
    API-->>U: balance: $30

    %% 4. Top up if needed
    alt Balance insufficient
        U->>API: POST /payments/topup {amount: 50}
        API->>Stripe: Create Checkout Session
        Stripe-->>API: checkout_url
        API-->>U: redirect to Stripe
        U->>Stripe: Pay $50
        Stripe->>API: Webhook: payment confirmed
        API->>DB: INSERT user_ledger (+50)
        DB-->>API: balance updated
        Note over DB: User.balance_user = $80
    end

    %% 5. Purchase practice
    U->>API: POST /practices/{id}/purchase

    rect rgb(255, 245, 235)
        Note over API,DB: Double-Entry Transaction
        API->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
        API->>DB: INSERT user_ledger (-50)
        API->>DB: INSERT master_ledger (+50, frozen=true)
        API->>DB: INSERT purchase (pending)
        API->>DB: INSERT booking (confirmed)
        API->>DB: COMMIT
    end

    DB-->>API: booking created
    API-->>U: ✓ Booking confirmed

    %% 6. Notifications
    API->>Bot: Schedule reminders (24h, 1h, 10min)
    Bot-->>U: 🔔 Reminder 24h before
    Bot-->>U: 🔔 Reminder 1h before
    Bot-->>U: 🔔 Reminder 10min before

    %% 7. Check-in
    U->>API: POST /practices/{id}/checkin {mood: "high"}
    API->>DB: INSERT checkin
    DB-->>API: ✓
    API-->>U: Check-in saved

    %% 8. Join practice
    U->>API: POST /bookings/{id}/join
    API->>DB: UPDATE booking (joined_at)
    DB-->>API: ✓
    API-->>U: Joined practice

    %% 9. Practice completes
    Note over API,DB: Master marks practice as completed

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over API,DB: Unfreeze + Commission
        API->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
        API->>DB: UPDATE master_ledger (frozen=false)
        API->>DB: INSERT master_ledger (-7.50, commission)
        API->>DB: INSERT company_ledger (+7.50)
        API->>DB: UPDATE purchase (completed)
        API->>DB: UPDATE practice (completed)
        API->>DB: COMMIT
    end

    Note over DB: Master: available_amount = $42.50

    %% 10. Feedback
    U->>API: POST /practices/{id}/feedback {rating: "fire"}
    API->>DB: INSERT feedback
    DB-->>API: ✓
    API-->>U: Thank you!

    Note over U,Bot: Journey completed ✓
